{"tid":1146241,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"利物浦絕地反擊 成文翠珊在英國國會討論話題","createTime":"2019-05-09T06:38:57.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-09T07:46:39.000Z","uid":54373,"like":16,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"3fa2d14c2b8ea76f609f70b44f837090a7db8540","tid":1146241,"uid":54373,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-09T06:38:57.000Z","msg":"【利物浦絕地反擊成英國國會話題】<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.google.com/url?sa=t&amp;rct=j&amp;q=&amp;esrc=s&amp;source=web&amp;cd=2&amp;cad=rja&amp;uact=8&amp;ved=2ahUKEwiVxPvZ6o3iAhWEd94KHeFFBkwQwqsBMAF6BAgJEAc&amp;url=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2FRTHKVNEWS%2Fvideos%2F1992717631022758%2F&amp;usg=AOvVaw0RWl7dE2bL5gipYadcoPkX\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.google.com%2Furl%3Fsa%3Dt%26rct%3Dj%26q%3D%26esrc%3Ds%26source%3Dweb%26cd%3D2%26cad%3Drja%26uact%3D8%26ved%3D2ahUKEwiVxPvZ6o3iAhWEd94KHeFFBkwQwqsBMAF6BAgJEAc%26url%3Dhttps%253A%252F%252Fwww.facebook.com%252FRTHKVNEWS%252Fvideos%252F1992717631022758%252F%26usg%3DAOvVaw0RWl7dE2bL5gipYadcoPkX&d=oAUO7kpDmgkuxlfprI4EYWhNlLB%2BLbsdBqu6cuXqlDc%3D&h=63f32333\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.google.com/url?sa=t&amp;rct=j&amp;q=&amp;esrc=s&amp;source=web&amp;cd=2&amp;cad=rja&amp;uact=8&amp;ved=2ahUKEwiVxPvZ6o3iAhWEd94KHeFFBkwQwqsBMAF6BAgJEAc&amp;url=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2FRTHKVNEWS%2Fvideos%2F1992717631022758%2F&amp;usg=AOvVaw0RWl7dE2bL5gipYadcoPkX</a><br />\n<br />\n歐聯四強次回合，利物浦主場4:0大勝巴塞羅那，絕地反擊成功，以總比數4:3勝出，晉身決賽。英國工黨黨魁郝爾彬說，首相文翠珊或許可以從利物浦領隊高普身上取得「貼士」，如何在歐洲取得好成績。文翠珊回應指，如果大家團結，仍然可以取得成功。"},{"pid":"3290d1fdb05479fc78f244bbe8fbbd28d78f90fb","tid":1146241,"uid":47496,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3fa2d14c2b8ea76f609f70b44f837090a7db8540","tid":1146241,"uid":54373,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-09T06:38:57.000Z","msg":"【利物浦絕地反擊成英國國會話題】<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.google.com/url?sa=t&amp;rct=j&amp;q=&amp;esrc=s&amp;source=web&amp;cd=2&amp;cad=rja&amp;uact=8&amp;ved=2ahUKEwiV